{"tid":915493,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"辣椒油定辣椒醬","createTime":"2018-11-25T04:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T00:51:53.000Z","uid":95457,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b22bb1b45a86163905f82b0d24ba16b5f215ad05","tid":915493,"uid":95457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T04:44:42.000Z","msg":"成日飲茶都要叫曬兩樣 <br />\n因為覺得有蒸既點心好似燒賣蝦餃要點辣椒油<br />\n煎既好似蘿蔔糕 要點辣椒醬<br />\n<br />\n硬係覺得如果撈亂黎點係好奇怪<br />\n定係得我咁奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9036cadf027f15ccfb353c05c3e3e8bec568a340","tid":915493,"uid":119347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T04:48:16.000Z","msg":"你不是一個人"},{"pid":"5bf55b7a214884e329c7b0141d978915d7a529ab","tid":915493,"uid":158372,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:05:35.000Z","msg":"辣椒油攞嚟淋,醬攞嚟點"},{"pid":"91c01e8ebe345f454ed470f70240bd150394c4de","tid":915493,"uid":45431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"絕對無問題 係要分"},{"pid":"42b1ddcb0004284f20b6e3d054e1bf98286ba98b","tid":915493,"uid":2110,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:28:38.000Z","msg":"你令我諗起強國北方人，食乜都加老乾媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蝦餃燒賣就咁食先係最好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae2bdb838f3885cadb971df2bdb2abff6c55e1d","tid":915493,"uid":181719,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:29:27.000Z","msg":"辣椒油啲渣先係王道"},{"pid":"6bf63842b04cecdd8afe65bb794b46e54897eab2","tid":915493,"uid":95457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42b1ddcb0004284f20b6e3d054e1bf98286ba98b","tid":915493,"uid":2110,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:28:38.000Z","msg":"你令我諗起強國北方人，食乜都加老乾媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji